  "title": "A stationary UFO spotted in Recife-PE [1972]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/07/18/a-stationary-ufo-spotted-in-recife-pe-1972/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-1Hj",
  "content": "<p class=\"p2\" style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"color:#99ccff;\"><strong>NOV 31st, 1972. Translation of a telegraphed message sent from a Police Department in Recife-PE to the Ministry of Aeronautics.</strong></span></p>\n<h5 class=\"p2\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">&#8220;<em>I inform that from 02:00 am to 04:00 am in the morning, during a party at America Club in this city [Recife], people of credibility [&#8230;] and many other people saw a strange object in an ovoid shape, luminous, which stayed stationary in space for a long time, quickly disappearing. Greetings. / JMC 1TEN &#8211; D.P./</em> &#8220;</h5>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo ‘Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)’. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.139. “Aparecimento de um objeto estranho, forma ovóide, luminoso</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">”. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our ‘Info’ page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [“Código de Referência”] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span>&lt;</p>\n",
  "excerpt": "<p>NOV 31st, 1972. Translation of a telegraphed message sent from a Police Department in Recife-PE to the Ministry of Aeronautics. &#8220;I inform that from 02:00 am to 04:00 am in the morning, during a party at America Club in this city [Recife], people of credibility [&#8230;] and many other people saw a strange object in [&hellip;]</p>\n",
